{"tid":1821080,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動]1月12和你讀，無人知啊，要大家幫手啊 - 本日重開","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T04:11:24.000Z","uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17d7f41e92ebcb5a84541ed27d576e55747c6bef","tid":1821080,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXUq8Hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXUq8Hf.jpg&h=b7224a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eO3SOHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeO3SOHj.jpg&h=0e060f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月12 和你讀 免費派書活動<br />\n地點 灣仔ACO 2-7PM<br />\n2-4PM 為新書聚，可以黎攞書同問吓問題，睇下自己可以點幫手<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n請各區有心人自備背囊或環保袋<br />\n帶書返自己區 搵黃店、連儂放書<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n知己知彼，百戰百勝，<br />\n不知己，豈能勝？<br />\n<br />\n了解哲學思維有助邏輯上嘅辨證，<br />\n在這本首次被翻譯為中文的書中，<br />\n與起義有關的概念多不勝數，<br />\n書是免費的，<br />\n知識是無價的。<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持，呢本書我哋一班文學、翻譯、藝術人士譯左好耐㗎啦！自資印咗5000本，好需要你哋嘅幫忙去18區放書！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現正招募<br />\n<br />\n香港八大大學站員<br />\n站員職務：<br />\n1.指定時間到指定地點攞書、海報、膠紙 (有可能安排到直接將書送去各大學校園，如果安排到，麻煩報名嘅同學喺校園接應)<br />\n2.返自己校園揀位貼海報同擺書<br />\n3.影張靚相，影條靚片<br />\n4.搞掂<br />\n<br />\n香港十八區站員<br />\n站員職務：<br />\n1.指定時間到指定地點攞書、海報、膠紙<br />\n2.返自己區搵獨立嘅黃書店，問下可唔可以攞免費書，佢話得就留低書同海報<br />\n3.仲有書同海報淨底嘅話可以放喺連儂牆<br />\n4.影張靚相，影條靚片<br />\n5.搞掂<br />\n<br />\n有意嘅話可以喺個chat度留言，或send個訊息俾Admin @hktazz ，身邊有大學生嘅朋友不妨幫我地宣傳下，麻煩晒大家！<br />\n<br />\n本書我哋印緊5000本，一月9或10號就出到貨。再提多次，書係免費嘅！"},{"pid":"be0f378638f5414a58e280bd01626bbdc647fc1e","tid":1821080,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:04:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=3aeea817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"f7da5ada9138a85f68c8582cd122d9c4d241b525","tid":1821080,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1674ca102196ecec0549b972c6400034fa116958","tid":1821080,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc3ab7b4df71b896cf66b10e7ac52e4aa25d5e07","tid":1821080,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}